Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank goodness\Nyour injury wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto was relieved, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, you must be hungry.\NIs there something you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:16.94,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392,221)}The Battle Begins.\N Naruto vs. Sasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Battle Begins.{\i0}\N{\i1}Naruto vs. Sasuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI really don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there were opinions that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with the final exam being suspended,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,no one should pass\Nthis time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hear the late Third Hokage\Nhighly praised your match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he intended to recommend you\Nfor Chunin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The lords of other lands\Nwho observed the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the proctors were of\Nthe same opinion as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it's not in my place\Nto say this or that about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,strive to perform in a manner\Nthat is worthy of that headband...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!\NAs of today, you're a Chunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow...\N- Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you who's never motivated\Nlook respectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh, I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have a toast to celebrate\NShikamaru's promotion to Chunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat the meat before the toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it'd be a waste if it got burned, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of meat. Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now,{\i0}\N{\i1}I have no interest in you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your target is Naruto, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll end up in the hospital again, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how to savor the taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I eat a lot,\NI know how to savor properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Choji, that's the last piece of meat\Nthat I've been grilling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The last bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the conclusion and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,will become the meat with\Nthe greatest value that should be savored!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hand over\Nthis last bite to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you acting cool for,\Nyou idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes fun of you\Nbecause you're like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're just a fat\N- Ino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a taboo word!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A meal isn't a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax at a time like this at least.\NWhat a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vulgar... Dirty mouthed...{\i0}\N{\i1}Too lazy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if these guys{\i0}\N{\i1}will be okay from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In particular...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji. With you it's nothing but food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a little training sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky that your mind\Ndoesn't restrict what you eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it rough with a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to diet, Ino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls want to be seen as cute as possible\Nby the one they like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But that person might not always\Nlike a thin person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place,\Nmost boys don't like fat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that... They like thin girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And, vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be a little more conscious\Nof your body, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... She doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Men don't like thin women\Nas much as women think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,More likely men who like chubby women\Nare the most common.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And, vice versa... I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she'd be twice as popular
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,if she were to gain a little more weight\Ninstead of dieting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a funny guy, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're smart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're much more awesome\Nthan the likes of Sasuke or Neji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never even thought about that.\NI'm me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the only one\Nwho became a Chunin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Chunin Exam this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might be better\Nat fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have given up if\NI'd gotten into one with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But earlier,\NSensei told me that all I do is eat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I'm not progressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm me, I tell you. And you're you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stupid talking about how which is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry too much\Nabout what Asuma says...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should live naturally\Nand take things easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later! I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's starting to say\Nsome troublesome thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,like he's going to teach me\Na new Jutsu or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a good guy...Choji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Head for the Leaf Village, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You've made up your mind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm carrying out fitness training\Nto get ready for the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to return as soon as\NI can after the surgery, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't die\Nif you give up being a Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so fixated\Non being a Shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My everything is proving that\Neven I can become a fine Ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You might die. Even if you succeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dream, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...do you snap this much{\i0}\N{\i1}at the mention of Hokage's name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will be the heir to the name{\i0}\N{\i1}of Hokage, no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because, Hokage is my dream!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this village, promising children{\i0}\N{\i1}are being brought up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sarutobi Sensei... Sure enough,{\i0}\N{\i1}you were a wonderful Hokage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery is in the afternoon.\NGet ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lee! Are you prepared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some apples...\NYou like them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, doesn't it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? I wonder where I put the knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right in front of you, believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so lame, you getting all scatterbrained\Njust because you're in front of Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather hear lame\Nfrom anyone but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}U-zu-ma-ki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto 2K Barrage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summoning Jutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will...protect Sakura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I I give up, believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke... Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You rescued me from{\i0}\N{\i1}the Sand Ninja, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person who rescued you...{\i0}\N{\i1}was Naruto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are weak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you weak...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because you don't have enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I peeled it nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut it to make it easy to eat, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't have to glare\Nat me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me... Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Here you are,\Njust treated by Old Lady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if she's the Fifth Hokage\Nor whatever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she should have just minded\Nher own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying let's do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or have you chickened out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sasuke. Hey... What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, you say something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect, believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking\NI wanted to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, the both of you... Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's...this feeling?{\i0}\N{\i1}My lower belly feels tight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to fight you, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... I feel a thrill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's funny! I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think\NI can finally beat you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abducting Naruto is the No. 1 priority{\i0}\N{\i1}of our organization, Akatsuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\NDon't talk foolish, you failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be\Na failure forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now,{\i0}\N{\i1}I have no interest in you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You... A loser like you better\Nnot act all high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! It's unlike you to lose\Nyour cool and raise a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So uncharacteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be that you picked a fight\Nand then got scared, could it, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just bring it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your headband before that!\NI'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't even be able...\Nto put one knick on my forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this is a testament to fighting\Non equal terms as a Leaf Shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm saying stuff like that\Nis acting high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that we're equal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do! I've never once\Nthought that I'm inferior to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you remain weak!\NLittle Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be getting carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!
