Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tiger Seal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style! Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N -Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What is that Jutsu?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
